  "commit_message": "refactor(buildenv): replace GC root machinery with stat/fetch/retry loop (#4282)\n\n## Proposed Changes\n\nThe previous design protected against GC races during environment builds\nby\ncreating Nix GC root symlinks immediately after each package was\nfetched.\nThis was ineffective for three reasons: local roots don't protect paths\non a\nremote Nix daemon; the race window between root creation and the first\n`builtins.storePath` read inside `buildenv.nix` was never fully closed;\nand\nspawning one `nix build",
